<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="caption row justify-content-center mt-3 mb-4">
    <h2 class="text-center">Welcome to Vacation Match!</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="caption row justify-content-center">
    <h5 class="text-center">
    きっとあなたにピッタリの目的地が見つかるはず!<br>
    写真映え？グルメ？穴場スポット？<br>
    気になるワードで検索してみよう！<br>
    まずは投稿をチェック!<br>
    </h5>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-12 col-sm-6">
    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center">
      <% @post.each do |post| %>
        <div class="text-center m-3">
          <% if post.image.present? %>
            <%= image_tag post.image, size: '200x200', class: "mb-2" %><br>
          <% else %>
            <%= image_tag 'noimage.png' , size: '200x200', class: "mb-2" %><br>
          <% end %>
          <strong class="text-dark d-inline-block text-truncate" style="max-width: 200px;"><%= post.title %></strong>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

  <div class="text-right mr-5 mb-3">
    <%= link_to "もっと見る！＞＞", posts_path, class: "font-weight-bold text-primary" %>
  </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>